Method Detail

put

public void put(double tm,
                double val)
Adding data to set (sample or trajectory)

Parameters:
tm - For trajectory sets represents the time when a change in the trajectory function occurs.
val - For trajectory sets, represents the new value of the trajectory function; for smaple sets, represents a new sample value.

get

public void get(double[] tmVal)
         throws java.io.EOFException
Get a value from the output set. For both sample and trajectory sets. To read from start of for first time, run rewindSet() first. When end of file is reached, method will generate EOFException

Parameters:
tmVal - - a array double with two values tmVal[0] - time, tmVal[1] - value.
Throws:
java.io.EOFException
